frames.caption: A cute animated bunny with a bright orange bow sits in a sunlit meadow, gazing at a butterfly hovering nearby. A basket filled with colorful flowers is placed beside the bunny, adding to the vibrant scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a whimsical and serene meadow setting, showcasing an animated bunny interacting with nature. The atmosphere is cheerful and lively, with a focus on the interaction between the bunny and the butterfly.

frames.caption: A cute, fluffy bunny with an orange bow sits in a sunlit meadow, gazing at a butterfly fluttering above. A basket of colorful flowers is placed beside the bunny, adding to the serene and whimsical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a charming, animated setting in a sunlit meadow. The focus is on a small bunny adorned with an orange bow, sitting beside a basket of vibrant flowers. A butterfly gracefully flutters above, capturing the bunny's attention.
